cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper is about a deep learning model for semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel transfer learning approach, which involves learning from limited labeled data and transferring knowledge to new categories with only image-level annotations. This suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or multimedia (cs.MM).
